{"id": "1182610003576762368", "channel_id": "1182610003576762368", "type": 0, "author_id": "921442534411100191", "author_name": "07_youer", "author_bot": false, "content": "個人建議將經驗也一併放在獎勵預覽處（橙色位置）\n然後加上今日獲得的經驗，舉例：60/240（藍色位置）\n\n大概這樣，具體位置可以再調整，因為要點擊玩法規則才發現能獲得經驗和今天獲得的額度，這樣的提示蠻不明顯的，有時會忽略掉。\n\n有人25等了今天才發現ww（對就是我）。", "timestamp": "2023-12-08T09:09:56.684000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1182610003853574205", "filename": "Screenshot_20231208_170152.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 114945, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1182610003576762368/1182610003853574205/Screenshot_20231208_170152.jpg?ex=6a004b64&is=69fef9e4&hm=8f12634efe44068a53ffdd48645550013676689a5b99230886bef55b57caecec&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1182610003576762368", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」幻夢深潛 經驗提示", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
